      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以账户创建是从EMR同步触发的。那创建之后第一个状态是什么？是Registered还是直接Active？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
