        "Email/identity verified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Registered和Active都画好了。那Active之后有哪些分支？异常流程也要考虑进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Active可以走到两个负面状态：Suspended和Deactivated。Suspended是策略违规或者支付问题导致的，Deactivated则是用户主动注销或者管理员操作。Suspended之后如果问题解决可以回到Active，也可以直接走到Deactivated。",
      "elements_involved": [
